      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IMAGINE THE FUN (8) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 2 lengths from Mad Maverick in third (22.67) at Gawler. The form from her last run stacks up well. Likely to feature again. BINNAWAY PEARL (5) is progressing well scoring last time out (16.67) at Murray Bridge and bringing up her 18th career win. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from eight starts. In top form and looks a key chance again. ICE AGE (4) has a superb record at this track and trip, unbeaten so far from five starts. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (16.63) in a Grade 2/3/4 over 300m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. RED SAID SO (7) cannot be ruled out.",
